		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="403" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津进行两段斩击，分别造成<span color="#ffacff">16.6%,<br/>25%</span><span>伤害，之后中手丢出雷钴，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">16.6%</span><span>伤害，片刻后雷钴爆炸，造成</span><span color="#ffacff"><br/>33.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="447" width="430" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">处在祸津后方时，其转身用刀斩造成<span color="#ffacff">66.6%</span><span>伤害，在斩击的轨迹上将降下落雷，每道造成</span><span color="#ffacff">8.3%</span><span>伤害，之后中手丢出雷钴，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">16.6%</span><span>伤害，片刻后雷钴爆炸，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">33.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="703" width="439" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津先朝上纵劈，产生5道快速移动的纵雷刃，造成<span color="#ffacff">25%</span><span>伤害，再朝右横劈一刀，产生1道慢速的横雷刃，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害；在近处，若被刀劈到则每次额外造成</span><span color="#ffacff">25%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="959" width="424" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">施放时，50%概率为该技能；祸津召唤两个手眼，手眼位置同步于玩家，几秒后两个手眼合击造成<span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1215" width="439" height="200" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津移至场地中心，召唤3个大型的雷钴落下，造成<span color="#ffacff">25%</span><span>伤害，其呈三角形摆布；雷钴将持续产生地波扩散，其造成</span><span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。<br/>地波沿顺时针方向产生，持续2轮，第3轮中，3个雷钴将全部产生地波，随后全部损坏。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1535" width="1003" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津御建转变为对付「永恒」之敌的形态，进入恶耀影向天魔状态，击飞附近的玩家不造成伤害，展开<span textDecoration="underline">恶耀魔甲</span><span>，每5s汲取玩家20能量(特殊能量不受影响)。</span><span color="#a4ffcc">退出状态后恢复全队元素能量与特殊能量。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/祸津御建鸣神命3.assets/Image_15.png')" x="1268" y="1163" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/祸津御建鸣神命3.assets/Image_16.png')" x="1248" y="1142" blendMode="normal">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1215" width="439" height="229" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津移至场地中心，<span color="#ffdfbf">清空角色的所有元素能量和特殊能量</span><span>并消失，留下一个</span><span color="#ffbfff">「</span><span textDecoration="underline" color="#ffbfff">追忆花团</span><span color="#ffbfff">」</span><span>，并随机标记一名玩家；稍后无想的一刀降下，并产生碎屏特效。若在护罩外，被标记的玩家将直接被</span><span color="#ffacff">击败</span><span>，未被标记的玩家受到</span><span color="#ffacff">66.6%</span><span>伤害，若在护罩内，则所有玩家只受到</span><span color="#ffacff">1</span><span>伤害，以上伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">闪避帧均无效</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="959" width="432" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">施放时，50%概率为该技能；祸津召唤一道黑影原地跟踪玩家，接触持续造成<span color="#ffacff">8.3%</span><span>伤害，片刻后黑影处钻出手眼，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">16.6%</span><span>伤害，再拍下，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">33.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="423" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津握住刀柄，施放拔刀斩，造成<span color="#ffacff">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="437" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">祸津高举刀，在前方长矩形区域劈下，造成<span color="#ffacff">116.6%</span><span>伤害；在周身产生持续的等离子场，持续造成</span><span color="#ffacff">8.3%</span><span>伤害</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="703" width="422" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离祸津较远时，其立即冲过来劈一刀，造成<span color="#ffacff">16.6%</span><span>伤害，劈后立即产生次元斩，依次造成</span><span color="#ffacff">8.3%,8.3%,33.3%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
