		<RichText x="66" y="1320" width="436" height="97" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">恶耀魔甲：<span color="#ffacff">96雷</span><span>盾，击破可移除抗性，使祸津退出恶耀影向天魔状态并眩晕；与其发生元素反应可产生3枚全元素微粒，CD1.5s；每10s，将失去</span><span color="#ffacff">8雷</span><span>盾。<br/>追忆花团：</span><span color="#ffacff">25雷</span><span>充能盾，雷元素攻击</span><span color="#ffacff">+25</span><span>/次，其他元素攻击</span><span color="#ffacff">+6.5</span><span>/次，其他攻击无效，击破展开护罩。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
